('Partnerships', 'Partnerships', '', 'Stakeholder Management', 'Understands the importance of stakeholder relationships and can identify key contacts with guidance. Interacts courteously and professionally but relies on others to manage and deepen relationships.', 'Actively builds and maintains positive relationships with stakeholders. Communicates effectively, demonstrates reliability, and fosters mutual trust to support collaborative outcomes.', 'Develops and nurtures long-term, trust-based relationships with key stakeholders. Adapts communication styles, manages complex interactions, and leverages relationships to drive shared success.', 'Serves as a strategic relationship leader, shaping stakeholder engagement strategies across teams or the organization. Builds networks of influence, resolves complex stakeholder challenges, and mentors others in effective relationship management.'),
('Partnerships', 'Partnerships', '', 'Coachability', 'Listens to feedback but may feel defensive or unsure how to apply it. Shows initial willingness to improve when guided by others.', 'Actively seeks feedback to improve performance and takes ownership of applying it. Responds positively to constructive input and makes visible efforts to adapt behaviors.', 'Demonstrates high receptivity to feedback and integrates it into ongoing professional growth. Encourages open dialogue and models a positive attitude toward continuous learning.', 'Leads a feedback-driven culture by actively modeling openness, adaptability, and self-improvement. Encourages others to seek, share, and apply feedback to strengthen team performance.'),
('Partnerships', 'Partnerships', '', 'Sales Methodologies', '', '', '', ''),
